releaseNotes:
How to use:
- In order to insert/update/delete: 
+ Create your own UnitOfWork that extends Kolabs.Repository.Dapper.UnitofWork and contains your repositories.
+ Repositories should be extended from Kolabs.Repository.Dapper.GenericRepository (basic functions: insert/update/delelte are already implemented)

using (var uow = new UnitOfWork(connectionString)) {
  uow.Repository.Add(entity);

  uow.Commit();
}
- Searching repositories should be extended from Kolabs.Repository.Dapper.GenericReadOnlyRepository which implemented functions: FindById. FineOne, Find...
class User : BaseEntity
{
	public Username { get; set; }
}
class UserRepository : Kolabs.Repository.Dapper.GenericReadOnlyRepository<User>, IUserRepository
{
}

using:
var _userRepository = new UserRepository("User", connectionString);
var user = _userRepository.Find(p => p.Username == "username");

